  "title": "Alphabet Q1 2026 Earnings Call",
  "datetime": "2026-04-24T20:00:00Z",
  "period": "CY2026_Q1",
  "location": "Mountain View, CA",
  "url": "https://abc.xyz/investor/",
  "turns": [
    {
      "speaker_id": "sundar-pichai",
      "speaker_name": "Sundar Pichai",
      "speaker_role": "CEO",
      "timestamp": "00:01:00",
      "text": "Q1 2026 continued the strong momentum we built through 2025. Google Cloud revenues grew 27% to $20.6 billion, exceeding our guidance. We launched Project Astra, our multimodal AI assistant, to general consumer availability in March, with over 80 million downloads in the first three weeks. Our AI search capabilities now generate AI-assisted answers for over 40% of all Search queries globally. We expect full-year 2026 Cloud revenue to reach $82 billion."
    },
    {
      "speaker_id": "anat-ashkenazi",
      "speaker_name": "Anat Ashkenazi",
      "speaker_role": "CFO",
      "timestamp": "00:18:00",
      "text": "Total Q1 2026 revenues were $118.6 billion, up 17% year-over-year. Operating margin was 37.8%, ahead of our 38% full-year target run rate. YouTube revenues grew 11% to $11.2 billion, with the ad-supported tier now representing 65% of total viewing time. We are raising our full-year capex guidance to $68 billion to support continued AI infrastructure expansion."
    },
    {
      "speaker_id": "operator",
      "speaker_name": "Operator",
      "speaker_role": "Operator",
      "timestamp": "00:38:00",
      "text": "Our next question comes from Eric Sheridan at Goldman Sachs."
    },
    {
      "speaker_id": "analyst-eric-sheridan",
      "speaker_name": "Eric Sheridan",
      "speaker_role": "Analyst",
      "timestamp": "00:38:20",
      "text": "Sundar, Project Astra is a major consumer bet. How are you thinking about the monetization pathway relative to Search, and does it cannibalize or complement the Search business?"
    }
  ],
